@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@companyId = REPLACE_COMPANY_ID
@authToken = REPLACE_BEARER_TOKEN

### Resetar trava de alteração do dia de cobrança (Super Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/master/companies/{{companyId}}/billing-day/reset-lock
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Sincronizar empresa com Asaas (Super Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/master/companies/{{companyId}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Atualizar dia de cobrança (Usuário dono da empresa)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/business/billing/day
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day": 15
}
